        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks CVN for reference to the <hi rend="italic">Comptes Rendus</hi> [<hi rend="italic">Académie Française</hi>].</p>  
<p>Mentions CVN’s work on Cucurbitaceae and notes that he (CD) has quoted extensively from it in <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>.</p>  
<p>Hopes to send paper on <hi rend="italic">Lythrum</hi> [<hi rend="italic">Collected papers</hi> 2: 106–31] soon.</p> 
            <p>Mentions exchange of photographs.</p>
        </abstract>
